column1: “Tonight the whole world is watching America. And I believe at our best America is a beacon for the globe...We will lead not only by the example of our power but by the power of our example” said President-elect Biden.
“Tonight the whole world is watching America”...Pres Elect Biden
Tonight’s debate showed clear differences.  Trump continues to showcase his wall on border with Mexico .  Biden commits to immigration reform and support for our dreamers.  Go Biden!!
